org.mmbase.util.functions

Class ReturnType<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mmbase.core.AbstractDescriptor
      • org.mmbase.util.functions.Parameter<C>
        • org.mmbase.util.functions.ReturnType<C>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Descriptor, PublicCloneable<AbstractDescriptor>

    public class ReturnType<C>
extends Parameter<C>
implements Serializable
    Description of the return type of certain function. This wraps a Class object but it has some extra members. Can be used as a constructor argument of Function objects or as an argument of Function.setReturnType(org.mmbase.util.functions.ReturnType<R>).
    Since:
    MMBase-1.7
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Daniel Ockeloen, Michiel Meeuwissen
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
